EigenMeat.EigenMaze
Class Preferences

java.lang.Object
  EigenMeat.EigenMaze.Preferences
public class Preferences
extends java.lang.Object

Preferences is a singleton soft-loaded class that contains values of global engine variables that are usually hardcoded. Use of the Preferences object and the SoftLoader to save settings to disk can allow for customization appropriate to each user's own system.
